A '''Chinese wedding album''' is an elaborate book of pictures that became a part of s in the late 20th century.
The album usually consists of many pictures of the  and  taken at various locations with many different costumes. In , these costumes often include wedding costumes belonging to different cultures, including  and  wedding costumes.
In contrast to Western wedding pictures, the Chinese wedding album usually does not contain pictures of the actual ceremony and wedding itself.  In , however, pictures of the ceremony and wedding are taken as well.